!.vine/knowledge/
!.vine/projects/
!.vine/scripts/
.vine/projects/*/*/PAUSE.md
.vine/PROFILE.md
# Personal overlay layer — gitignored by design (absent .local changes nothing)
.vine/context/*.local.md

